author: @Necroherz
text:
✦ Everyone wishing a happy birthday to Mark and Doyoungie calling him "Our angel" awww our sweet bunny 🥺💚
✦ Tyong being so cute, bubbly, sweet, babygirly talking to the camera but as soon as he has to start recording for the mv his bad boy moth3rfvcker bed breaker self appears oh yeah 🔥🔥🔥
✦ Aww they even took some time to celebrate Mark's birthday, bringing a cake a singing it the HB song in english. Now that cute little boy of 17 is turning 24 i can't believe how fast the time passes 🥺 and our bunny hugging him from the stomach doing it so cute and timid i can't!!! That was definitely the most cute scene i have ever seen 😭💚
✦ The Dreamies, i mean Renjun, Jeno and Chenle and even their manager coming to the set there in the roof to also wish Mark a happy birthday 🥺 and then preparing him a birthday cake that is actually a watermelon, Junnie saying that is filled with NCT Dream's love and Chenle that what is more important here is their heart and intention i mean there is no doubt ✨
✦ The ending result was Mark not wanting to let off Jeno and Renjun 💚
✦  Ten coming to shoot and leaving with no interactions on camera with the members nor even talking a bit to us but at least was there to also celebrate Marks special day 💔. Day 2 of the Baggy Jeans music video filming and it seems like Ten is more motivated  and played the bottle of water challenge with Mark.
✦ Doyoungie posing on top of that billiard table like a siren or Titanic's Rose i don't but i was mesmerized all those second with his gracefulness. ALSO HAVE ANYONE ELSE NOTICED HOW SWEET AND HAPPY WAS OUR BUNNY THE ENTIRE DAYS OF FILMATION!! That made me even happier 💚
✦ Jaehyun doing everything in sexy as always. Man, everything he does no matter how simply and trivial could be it looks so damn sexy 🫠 
      - Please, can Jae's stylists stop this trend of hers, like we get that you girls like to style his hair covering his forehead. That you find him like that even cuter but our opinion should also be considered and we want to see it and all combed back like for the Two Baddies comeback 
      - So the mystery of Jaehyun's sexily biting that cristal billiard ball was that it was actually a plum... I thought it was a chunk of white chocolate covered in edible blue color coat of some kind of sugar 
✦ Ten came and started to record his solo verse fully displaying his "I'm the actual president of the babygirlism here" in all his majesty. So delicate, fluid, graceful that is somehow also kind of seductive, attractive, erotic and inviting... Or it is just me drooling over him... I think that is possible too 😅
   - Fun fact, once again, i'm fvcking in love with his nose line. Right side, left side, frontally or whatever the angle the camera guy can record him. Like is so precious and perfectly made... Now i'm a weirdo....
✦ So they actually had the same director of The 7th Sense and Simon Says music videos that makes even meaningful this reunion unit for Baggy Jeans 
✦ Act 1. Ten sharing the same brain cell with us thinking and appreciating how cool (And sexy) looked Doyoung in that croptop 😏 and Mark no letting Ten appear on camera really well 😒. Act 2. Ten now trying to flirt with the bunny, the bunny got actually scared and hopped away
✦  Mark trying to look like the toughest in every shoot but actually, for Baggy Jeans specially, he was the most babygirl in that outfit with the white sleeveless shirt, the head scarf and the jeans. Like for that TikTok he was really feeling himself 😅 we loved it 💚
✦ Our actor Kim Doyoung showing off his acting skills and Mark playing along following him in the impromptu was the cutest and most memorable scene haha i'll actually cut that scene of this bts video and keep it for the posterity 💚... Is our bunny actually hinting us that his next drama role will be a surgeon or something like that in a medic genre 🤨
✦ I thought the "ghosts" using the baggy jeans were completely made by cgi. Like, i thought that Mark was dancing alone but in reality they had a dancer with a green shirt doing it and then post-production just edit him leaving only the pants 
✦ Finally the most shocking and iconic naked scene with our 0 muscle slim unit haha i mean i appreciate the courage but it seems like Tyong liked it so much since we saw him throwing his tank tops at the NCT Nation there in Japan over and over again almost all of our neos did it so it's ok haha  😏💚

author: @markys99
text: O Ten de fato brilhou nessa era. Eu sei que todos foram incríveis e cada um teve o seu momento de brilhar, mas falando especificamente do Chitta, eu acho que não só a música como o MV, os figurinos, e até a coreografia combinaram com ele. De fato, ele deu tudo de si nos stages e eu vi ele brilhar no palco. Ele foi de longe o que eu mais elogiei nos stages, SKKSKSSK! (apesar dos outros também terem sido incríveis!). Eu realmente não poupo elogio pro Ten, porque sei que ele merece e admiro todo o talento dele e a pessoa que ele é. Um artista INCRÍVEL que merece ser chamado de Artista. Ten/10💚🛐

author: @markys99
text: Ter videos sobre os bastidores dos mvs deveria ser de lei pra TODOS os grupos de kpop. Eu fico tão feliz vendo que mesmo cansados de gravar as cenas, eles ainda se divertem. O carinho que eles têm pelo Mark, aaaaa! Até os meninos do Dream vieram pra parabenizar ele. Markinhos é um tesouro, uma verdadeira beldade, nunca vi alguém tão gentil, carinhoso e talentoso quanto ele. Amo demais🤧💚

author: @markys99
text: Cara, de verdade, na minha opinião esse foi um dos melhores lançamentos do NCT de todos os tempos. A música não só é boa como o MV é PERFEITO e tem tantos elementos e detalhes que alguns eu só fui notar assistindo esse vídeo. Além da coreografia também ser uma peça chave e o MV estar RECHEADO de referências à The 7th sense, SIMPLESMENTE GENIAL.🛐
